    "location": "scripts/ai_agent_bridge/_cli.py:678",
    "description": "The new proxy is documented as localhost-only, but the CLI exposes `--host` directly to `uvicorn.run` without rejecting non-loopback values or requiring an explicit remote-access opt-in. Since the service has no authentication and can launch local agent CLIs from incoming requests, `ab serve --openai --host 0.0.0.0` can expose a local subprocess execution bridge to the network by accident."
  },
